  "180 degrees": "",
  "25 degrees": "",
  "90 degrees": "",
  "45 degrees": "",
  "25% of 360 degrees = 0.25 x 360 = 90 degrees.": "",
  "Pie charts are NOT appropriate when:": "",
  "Categories do not represent parts of a single whole": "",
  "You have categorical data": "",
  "The data has percentages": "",
  "You want to show proportions": "",
  "Pie charts should only be used when categories are mutually exclusive parts of a single whole that sum to 100%.": "",
