  "Categories can be combined arbitrarily": "",
  "Each observation belongs to exactly one category, so slices do not overlap": "",
  "Categories can overlap so data falls in multiple slices": "",
  "All categories must have equal size": "",
  "For a valid pie chart, each data point must belong to exactly one category so the slices form a non-overlapping partition of the whole.": "",
