  "What does 'percentage label' on a pie chart communicate?": "",
  "The exact proportion of the whole that each category represents": "",
  "The frequency of each category": "",
  "The total number of observations": "",
  "The central angle of each slice": "",
  "Percentage labels show readers the exact share each category represents, since estimating proportions visually from slice size alone can be inaccurate.": "",
