  "A legend maps each color or pattern to its corresponding category name, helping readers identify what each slice represents.": "",
  "What does it mean to 'aggregate small categories' in a pie chart?": "",
  "Adding new categories to the chart": "",
  "Making small slices larger than they should be": "",
  "Removing small categories entirely": "",
